item.title: Prayer bpn12985 in Kuanua
item.description: I - ia ra Luluai nina na takvue ra umana vartup? Da vatangia: Pite pa u a Luluai ! Nam ra Luluai ! Diat par kana umana bul kudakudar ma diata mur kana umana varkurai. (Source category: A NIARING UPI RA MARAMARAVUT) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12985)
